# ML-Based Adaptive Learning System for Neurodiverse Students

## Overview

This project predicts a student's preferred learning style and provides adaptive recommendations for visual, audio, and text-based learning support.

## Project Structure

```text
project-folder/
|-- frontend/   # React + Vite frontend
|-- backend/    # Flask API
|-- ml/         # Model training scripts and saved models
|-- analysis/   # Analysis scripts and generated charts
|-- dataset/    # CSV datasets
|-- README
```

## Run The Project

### Backend

```powershell
python backend/api.py
```

### Frontend

```powershell
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

## API Endpoint

```text
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/predict
```
